```

### Key other type exports:
- `ColumnConfig<TData, TType, TVal, TId>` -- the column configuration object (id, accessor, displayName, icon, type, options, etc.)
- `ColumnDataType` = `"text" | "number" | "date" | "option" | "multiOption"`
- `FilterOperators` -- maps each data type to its operator union (e.g. `text` -> `"contains" | "does not contain"`)
- `ColumnOption` -- `{ label: string; value: string; icon?: ... }`
- `DataTableFilterActions` -- interface with `addFilterValue`, `removeFilterValue`, `setFilterValue`, `setFilterOperator`, `removeFilter`, `removeAllFilters`
- `FilterStrategy` = `"client" | "server"`
- Utility types: `ElementType<T>`, `Nullable<T>`, `FilterValues<T>`, `ColumnDataNativeMap`

**There are NO utility functions exported from this file** -- it is purely a type definition file. All utility functions live in `lib/` and `core/`.

